text: Erlangen-Höchstadt (German: Landkreis Erlangen-Höchstadt, East Franconian: Landgrais Erlang-Heegschdôdd) is a Landkreis (district) in Bavaria, Germany. The main river is the Regnitz, which runs through the city of Erlangen. ==Towns and municipalities== Towns Municipalities #Baiersdorf #Herzogenaurach #Höchstadt #Adelsdorf #Aurachtal #Bubenreuth #Buckenhof #Eckental #Gremsdorf #Großenseebach #Hemhofen #Heroldsberg #Heßdorf #Kalchreuth 12.
